title: YES it’s Oh Dem Again!!! Annual toy/donation drive
desc: Come Share the love as we give back to the less fortunate.? Come chill for the day with us as we listen to some music, play cards, and dominoes. Bring a toy, school supplies, toiletries, reading books, luggage, or a donation for a foster child in need this holiday season. (Newborn to 18 years) ****Feel free to drop off donations now until the above date Free Admission DONATIONS WILL BE GIVEN TO ONE OR MORE FOSTER HOME AT CHRISTMAS
